name: PROPERTIES 06 -Duplex in Little Nostalgia
description:
The following NFT corresponds to the collection of properties located in Kitty City in the Little Nostalgia neighborhood.
This property is divided in two, each part has a bedroom, a large living-dining room and two balconies in common, generating a meeting space between neighbors, where sharing a cup of tea and barbecue becomes something usual for the weekends. Cat visits are extremely frequent due to the particular view offered by the small main balcony of the central square of Little Nostalgia.
The environments are cozy and maintain the temperature due to its wide/thick brick walls, in addition to its two fireplaces that manage to heat the entire house in twenty minutes.
Land measurements: 60m x 70m
